}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The OUI is that of [http://www.sunrichtech.com.hk/ '''Sunrich Technology''']. :The serial number also is prefixed by '''SUN'''. They would seem to be the manufacturer of the device.
The device's box has the device branded as an '''InfoZone''' U-790. :[http://www.sunrichtech.com.hk/assign.asp?keyid=ba12 U-790] is the model of '''Sunrich''''s USB 3.0 Ethernet dongle on their site.
